Text: So far so good -- except I've been stuck at 93.9% for a few hours. But as soon as I logged in, my download speed increased. The audio files that have finished downloading look good, and the other ones should get done eventually, which is great. Thanks!

Can someone else get on and seed this? Right now I'm the only seeder, and I've been stuck at 93.9% for more than a day now, so if someone else doesn't get on, we're all going to be stuck missing the last 6.1% of the files.
